The paper discusses recent advances in language modeling and focuses on the Machine Reading Comprehension task, which falls under the categories of natural language processing, artificial intelligence, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
